ACP 2017

Wading into data-driven seas - ACP 2017 February 18, 2017 @ 10:00

http://bit.ly/2d79XfU

The rise of Big Data
---------
-The Information Age has flooded the Internet with digital data, produced on a massive scale
-It's not a fad, it's not going away

Using data to tell stories
---------
-Data journalism is a genre of reporting, but data is also tool in a journalists' toolbox
-Treat data like any other source. Ask it questions, verify what it says, use it to tell stories

Kinds of data-driven stories
---------
-Analyses
-Dataviz
-"Put a fact in every paragraph"

